{"type": "article", "id": 27501, "title": "鱼酱包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-30T07:04:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021425066DPzBHY3rhK5Nw7V.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>请不要误会，它并不是鱼味的牙膏，而是 <a href=\"http://bedow.se/\">Bedow</a> 为瑞典一间家族企业 Biggans 的鱼酱设计的包装。棕色纸板外盒印着海浪的图案，内部装有蓝绿底色的管状鱼酱，而当你翻到盒底的时候，还能惊喜地发现海星和水草，就好像潜到了海底一样。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142502uza8ytD6QYMZkAOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142503En1HULyiMZfzJuDT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142504uUFkrKbSWNfmtVYe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142505nIBgkK0b7O13wmqu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}